  "hadith0": "\"Camalada Alle ugu jecel waa kuwa si joogto ah loo sameeyo, xitaa hadday yar yihiin.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith2": "\"Marka uu dhinto wiilka Aadam, camalladiisu way joogsataa marka laga reebo saddex: sadaqo socota, cilmi anfaca, ama ilmo fiican oo u duceeya.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith3": "\"Qofkii tukada labada salaadood ee qabow (Fajriga iyo Casriga) wuxuu gali doonaa Jannada.\"\n— Bukhaari",
  "hadith4": "\"Allaahu ma eego muuqaalkaaga ama hantidaada, laakiin wuxuu eegaa qalbiyadaada iyo camalladaada.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith6": "\"Fududeeya hana adkeeynina; u bishaareya hana ka cabsiiynina dadka.\"\n— Bukhaari",
  "hadith7": "\"Qofkii jid u mara raadinta cilmiga, Allaahu wuxuu uga fududeeyaa jidka Jannada.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith8": "\"Sadaqadu hantida ma yareeyo.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith9": "\"Mu'minka xoogga badan waa ka fiican yahay oo Alle ka jecel yahay mu'minka daciifka ah, laakiin labadaba wanaag way ku jirtaa.\"\n— Muslim",
  "historyDayCompleted": "{completed} ka mid ah {total} la dhammeeyey",
