  "hadith53": "\"Ha quudhsin wax kasta oo wanaagsan, xitaa haddii ay tahay inaad walaalkaa kula kulanto waji bashbash ah.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith54": "\"Kuwiinna ugu wanaagsan waa ka ugu wanaagsan qoyskiisa.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith55": "\"Qofkii habeenkii akhriya labada aayad ee ugu dambeeya Suurada Al-Baqarah, waa ku filan yihiin.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith56": "\"Adduunyadani waa raashin, raashintii ugu fiicnaydna waa naag wanaagsan.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith57": "\"Saddex ducooyin ah oo aan la celin: ducada qofka sooman, hogaamiyaha cadliska ah, iyo qofka la dulmi jiray.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith58": "\"Qofkii hal mar salaad iigu diro, Ilaahay toban jeer buu naxariis ugu diraa.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith65": "\"Mu'minku waa muraayaddii mu'minka.\"\n— Abu Dawud",
  "hadith66": "\"Runtu waxay horseedaa wanaag, wanaaguna wuxuu horseedaa Jannada.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith67": "\"U celi amaanada qofka kugu aaminay, hana khiyaanayn qofka ku khiyaanay.\"\n— Abu Dawud & Tirmidhi",
  "hadith68": "\"Daal, cudur, murug, tiiraanyo, waxyeello ama walaac oo Muslim-ka gaaraya, xitaa qodax oo ku mudhda, Ilaahay wuxuu ku cafiyaa qaar ka mid ah dambiyaashiisa.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith69": "\"Ducada Muslimka uu u sameeyo walaalki isagoo maqan had iyo jeer waa la aqbalaa.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith70": "\"Qofkii saddex jeer Ilaahay ka waydiista Jannada, Jannadu waxay tidhaahdaa: Ilaahayow, Jannada geli.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith71": "\"Soonka ugu fiican ee ka dambeeya Ramadaan waa soonka bisha Ilaahay ee Muharram.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith72": "\"Qofkii xajka sameeya oo aan hadal xun ku hadlin dambina samayn, wuxuu u soo noqdaa sida maalin hooyadii dhashay.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith73": "\"Cumrada ilaa cumrada kale waa kafaarad dambiyada u dhexeeya.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith74": "\"Ku dhaqso camalka wanaagsan ka hor fitnooyin u imanaya sida qayb ka mid ah habeen madow.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith75": "\"Laba rakcadood ee salaadda Fajr way ka wanaagsan yihiin adduunka iyo waxa ku jira oo dhan.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith77": "\"Haddii aad Allaah ku tawakushaan sida loo tawakuli lahaa, wuxuu idinku rizqin lahaa sida uu u rizqeeyo shimbiraha.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith78": "\"Qofka booqda qof buka, wuxuu ku suganyahay beeraha Jannada ilaa uu soo noqdo.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith79": "\"Faafia salaamta, quudi dadka gaajaysan, salaadna tuka habeenkii markii dadku hurdo — Jannada nabad ku galaysaan.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith80": "\"Qofkii aan dadka u mahad naqi karin, Allaah na mahad naqayo.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith81": "\"Xasaddu waa la oggolaan karaa laba kiis oo keliya: nin Allaah maal siiyay oo jidka xaqa ku bixiya, iyo nin Allaah xigmad siiyay oo ku xukuma kuna baraa.\"\n— Bukhari & Muslim",
  "hadith82": "\"Qofku wuxuu ku socda diinta saaxiibkiis, sidaas darteed mid kastaaba ha eego qofka uu saaxiib la yahay.\"\n— Abu Dawud & Tirmidhi",
  "hadith85": "\"Qofkii u dhaafa wax Allaah daraaddiis, Allaah wuxuu ugu beddeli doonaa wax ka wanaagsan.\"\n— Ahmad",
  "hadith86": "\"Qofka qariiya ceebta Muslim, Allaah wuxuu qariinayaa ceebtiisa Maalinta Qiyaamaha.\"\n— Bukhari & Muslim",
  "hadith87": "\"Adduunkan ku jir sidii aad qariib tahay ama musaafir.\"\n— Bukhari",
  "hadith88": "\"Qofka u fududeeya qof dhibaato ku jira, Allaah wuxuu ugu fududeeyaa adduunka iyo aakhirada.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith89": "\"Abaalgudka camalku wuxuu ku xiran yahay niyada.\"\n— Bukhari & Muslim",
  "hadith90": "\"Ka fogaada tuhmada, waayo, tuhmadu waa hadalka ugu beenta badan.\"\n— Bukhari & Muslim",
  "hadith93": "\"Wada cuna oo magaca Allaah sheega, waxaa laydiin barakadeeyaa.\"\n— Abu Dawud",
  "hadith94": "\"Ma jiro koox fadhiista iyagoo xusaya Allaah ilaa ay malaa'igtu hareereeyaan, naxariistu qariso, xasilloonidu ku soo degto, oo Allaah ku xuso kuwa Agtiisa ah.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith95": "\"Allaah ma siiyo addoon cafinta sabab ahaan wax aan sharaf ahayn.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith96": "\"Geelahaaga xidh, kaddibna Allaah ku tawakul.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith97": "\"Waa lala yaabaa arrimaha mu'minka — wax walba waa u wanaagsan yihiin.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith98": "\"Muslimku waa walaalka Muslimka: ma dulmiyo, ma dayaco, mana quudhsado.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith20": "\"Qofkii sooma Ramadaan iimaankiisa iyo rajaynta ajar, dambiyadiisii hore waa loo cafiyaa.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith22": "\"Ducada u dhexaysa adhaamka iyo iqaamaddu lama diido.\"\n— Abu Dawud",
  "hadith23": "\"Qofkii Ilaahay u dhisa masjid, Ilaahay wuxuu ugu dhisaa guri Jannada.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith24": "\"Safafka ugu wanaagsan ee ragga waa kuwa hore, safafka ugu wanaagsan ee haweenka waa kuwa dambe.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith25": "\"Soomku waa gaashaan ka dhawra Naarta.\"\n— Nasaai",
  "hadith26": "\"Qofkii tukada laba iyo toban rakco oo sunno ah, guri ayaa loogu dhisaa Jannada.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith27": "\"Kan si fiican u akhriyo Quraanka wuxuu la jiri doonaa malaa'igta sharafta leh.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith29": "\"Sadaqada ugu wanaagsan waa biyaha cabbitaanka.\"\n— Ahmad",
  "hadith30": "\"Qofkii ka saara dhibaato mu'min, Ilaahay wuxuu ka saari dhibaato Maalinta Qiyaamada.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith32": "\"Xishmaddu waa qayb ka mid ah iimaanka.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith34": "\"Qofkii samiray, Ilaahay wuxuu siinayaa samir.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith36": "\"Midkiinna ma rumeynayo ilaa uu u jeclaado walaalihiis wuxuu naftiisa u jecel yahay.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith37": "\"Quudi kuwa gaajaysan, soo booqda kuwa buka, xoreena maxaabiista.\"\n— Bukhaari",
  "hadith38": "\"Qofka xoogga leh maaha kan ku guulaysta legdanka, waa kan is-xakama markuu cadhaysan yahay.\"\n— Bukhaari & Muslim",
  "hadith40": "\"Dhaha 'SubhanAllah', 'Alhamdulillaah' iyo 'Allaahu Akbar' saddex iyo soddon jeer kasta oo salaad ka dib.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith41": "\"Dhikriga ugu wanaagsan waa La ilaaha illallaah.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith42": "\"Waxaa jira labo nicmo oo ay dad badan khasaaraan: caafimaadka iyo waqtiga faariga ah.\"\n— Bukhaari",
  "hadith43": "\"Ka faa'iidaysta shan ka hor shan: yaranimo ka hor gaboob, caafimaad ka hor jirro, hodan ka hor faqri, waqti ka hor mashquul, iyo nolol ka hor dhimasho.\"\n— Hakim",
  "hadith44": "\"Qofkii akhriyo Suuradda Al-Ikhlaas toban jeer, Ilaahay wuxuu ugu dhisaa guri Jannada.\"\n— Ahmad",
  "hadith45": "\"Salaadda ugu wanaagsan ka dib fariidada waa salaadda habeenka.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith46": "\"Sadaqadu way demisaa dambiyada sida biyuhu ay demiyaan dabka.\"\n— Tirmidhi",
  "hadith47": "\"Kan xiriirka qaraabada xajiya maaha kan ku abtirsa, waa kan xajiya xitaa markay go'do.\"\n— Bukhaari",
  "hadith49": "\"Qofkii cuna oo yidhaahda: 'Mahad Allaah oo i siiyay cuntadan oo aan wax awood iyo xoog ah iigu samaynin ii soo fidiyey,' dambiyadiisii hore waa la cafiyaa.\"\n— Tirmidhi"
}
